title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Aug 17 2021

description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 1: Biden reads speech, resumes vacation as Afghanistan crumbles. How many Americans are trapped in Afghanistan? State Department spokesman to Taliban: Be Nice! Be inclusive! The State Department is a very left-wing place, many would trade in their American citizenship for international citizenship. Not many Democrats trying to carry water for Joe Biden right now. De Blasio "forces" Buck to get the shot. Here comes the covid booster shot! Fully vaccinated as a concept is now dead because they are telling you everyone needs boosters.
